race.description: Kia Ora Bloodlines To Headlines Handciap (Bm72)
race.comment: SEQUISTA (6) talented filly starting to put it all together. At her peak and will relish the fast tempo. Circled the field with a hard fought victory over 1300m at Wyong in similar company. Can measure up despite rising 2kg in weight. Go close. STORMLAND (4) progressive gelding capable of going on with it this time in. Drifted back in the field and came with a well timed run to score his second victory over 1100m at Canterbury. Meets a stronger field out to the 1200m and sure to be thereabouts. NEPO BABY (13) Lucky Vega filly resuming. Undefeated in two starts when winning by big margins in weaker grade. Scored a slick trial win at Tamworth over 905m. Ticks a few boxes and not to be underestimated. ZUMBO (11) was prominent at the turn on resumption with a gritty third in the heavy (8) going over 1100m at this track. Has further improvement to come with map favours. Value chance. SHELSTEIN (5) back in trip and can improve sharply at the big odds fourth-up.
